OL,3,CWorld Cup begins after star-studded
OL,4,Copening ceremony in Mexico City
OL,6,FThe largest World Cup in tournament
OL,7,Fhistory began on Thursday with a
OL,8,Fcolourful and star-studded opening
OL,9,Fceremony at the famous Azteca Stadium
OL,10,Fin Mexico City.
OL,12,FAmid escalating protests and social
OL,13,Ftensions in Mexico's capital, more
OL,14,Fthan 80,000 fans made their way to
OL,15,FAzteca Stadium, ahead of co-host
OL,16,FMexico's opening match against South
OL,17,FAfrica.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
