OL,3,CWorld Cup begins after star-studded
OL,4,Copening ceremony in Mexico City
OL,6,FIt got a much-needed facelift ahead of
OL,7,Fthe 48-team tournament that Mexico is
OL,8,Fhosting alongside the United States
OL,9,Fand Canada.
OL,11,FThe iconic venue will be the first
OL,12,Fstadium to host three World Cup
OL,13,Fopeners ` after doing so in the 1970
OL,14,Fand 1986 tournaments.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
