OL,3,CWorld Cup begins after star-studded
OL,4,Copening ceremony in Mexico City
OL,6,FUnder the shadow of a huge World Cup
OL,7,Ftrophy replica, Mexican pop-rock band
OL,8,FMana were the first to take the stage
OL,9,Ffor a musical performance.
OL,11,FThey were followed by Venezuelan
OL,12,Fsinger Danny Ocean and then Mexican
OL,13,Fartist Belinda.
OL,15,FColombian singer J Balvin also gave a
OL,16,Flengthy performance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
