OL,3,CWorld Cup begins after star-studded
OL,4,Copening ceremony in Mexico City
OL,6,FOne of the highlights of the show was
OL,7,Ffour-time Grammy winner Shakira
OL,8,Ftreating fans to a performance of the
OL,9,Fofficial World Cup song 'Dai Dai'
OL,10,Falongside Nigerian singer Burna Boy.
OL,12,FIt is the eighth opening match of a
OL,13,FWorld Cup for the Mexicans, who had
OL,14,Fpreviously lost five and drawn the
OL,15,Flast two, including against South
OL,16,FAfrica in the 2010 World Cup.
OL,18,FSouth Africa is playing in its first
OL,19,FWorld Cup since hosting the 2010
OL,20,Ftournament. The Bafana Bafana also
OL,21,Fplayed in the 1998 and 2002 editions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
