OL,3,CWorld Cup begins after star-studded
OL,4,Copening ceremony in Mexico City
OL,6,FMexico arrives with an eight-match
OL,7,Funbeaten streak and has not lost since
OL,8,Flast November, when Paraguay beat them
OL,9,Fin a friendly.
OL,11,FThe Mexican side is led by the 67-year-
OL,12,Fold coach Javier Aguirre, who is in
OL,13,Fhis third stint with the national team.
OL,15,FThursday's opening ceremony is one of
OL,16,Fthree and was created by the Italian
OL,17,Fproducer responsible for this year's
OL,18,FWinter Olympics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
