OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781229799
OL,3,CWorld Cup begins after star-studded
OL,4,Copening ceremony in Mexico City
OL,6,FThe opening ceremony also featured
OL,7,FShakira and Burna Boy, who performed
OL,8,Fthe official World Cup song "Dai Dai".
OL,10,FMexico's president Claudia Sheinbaum
OL,11,Fwas not in attendance, after deciding
OL,12,Fto boycott the World Cup matches in
OL,13,Fsolidarity with "ordinary Mexicans".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
